            [LOCKED CONTENT STARTS HERE]

            **1. Engineering & Technology:**
            * **Winner: JKUAT.**
            * *Why:* JKUAT was built for tech. Their labs in Juja are better equipped for practicals (Mechatronics, Civil, Agricultural Engineering). UoN is theory-heavy.
            
